---
import PageHero from "../../components/PageHero.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../../config/site.js";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy policy for MagicLens, including the current handling of uploads and final generated videos for the live guided experiences."
  path="/privacy/"
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Privacy Policy"
    lead="Effective date: March 13, 2026. This policy applies to the MagicLens website at ai-moments.com and explains the current operational truth behind the live guided experiences."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container legal-prose">
      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Our commitment to privacy</h2>
        <p>
          MagicLens is operated by {siteConfig.legalOperatorName}, a Canadian company. We aim to explain the current experience
          flows in plain language so visitors understand what happens to uploads, whether an account is required, and how long final
          generated videos remain available.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Information we do not retain</h2>
        <p>
          The live guided experiences begin from an uploaded source image. Under the current experience model, uploaded source photos
          are used during generation and are not retained after processing.
        </p>
        <p>
          MagicLens does not require account creation for the live guided experiences presented on this site today, so visitors are
          not asked to create a profile in order to start those flows.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Information we do retain</h2>
        <p>
          Final generated videos for the live guided experiences remain available for up to 60 days so families can access the
          delivered result. After that retention period, they are permanently deleted.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Third-party experience domains</h2>
        <p>
          The current live guided creation flows continue on separate experience domains, including santa-video.com,
          easterbunny-video.com, and toothfairy-video.com. MagicLens provides the shared discovery, positioning, and information
          layer for those experiences.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>
        <p>
          The live guided experiences are intended for family use. Parents and guardians should supervise children’s interaction with
          the experiences and any resulting content.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-card" data-reveal>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.supportEmail}`}>{siteConfig.supportEmail}</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
